# Title: Potential Vivaldi_elf.DLL Sideloading
# Author: X__Junior (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-08-03
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects potential DLL sideloading of "vivaldi_elf.dll"
# MITRE Tactic: Persistence
# Tags: attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.execution, attack.stealth, attack.t1574.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_side_load_vivaldi_elf.yml

ImageLoaded="*\\vivaldi_elf.dll" NOT (ImageLoaded="*\\Vivaldi\\Application\\*" Image="*\\Vivaldi\\Application\\vivaldi.exe")